      <title>就业数据增强美联储降息预期，美元或创今年最大单日跌幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/dollar-s-worst-day-this-year-shows-fed-bets-outweigh-haven-bid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美元出现自五月以来的最大跌幅，因美国劳动力报告意外疲软，加剧了人们对经济前景的担忧，导致交易员押注美联储今年将更积极地降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/dollar-s-worst-day-this-year-shows-fed-bets-outweigh-haven-bid</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 15:53:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
